{"word":"False Worship","slug":"false-worship","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>False Worship</b> - <b>(A) IDOLATRY</b><p/><b>(1) Forbidden</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=2'>Gen 35:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=20&verse=4'>Exo 20:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=17'>Exo 34:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=26&verse=1'>Lev 26:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=7&verse=25'>Deu 7:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=11&verse=16'>Deu 11:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=22'>Deu 16:22</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=81&verse=9'>Psa 81:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=42&verse=8'>Isa 42:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=5&verse=21'>1Jn 5:21</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Iconoclasm, RELIGIOUS REFORMS<p/> RELIGIOUS REFORMS<p/><b>(2) Prophecies concerning the Overthrow of</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=2&verse=20'>Isa 2:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=47'>Jer 51:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=5&verse=13'>Mic 5:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=13&verse=2'>Zec 13:2</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Worldwide Missions, MISSIONS<p/><b>(3) Idols Characterized,</b> as<p/><b>Insentiate</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=4&verse=28'>Deu 4:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=115&verse=4'>Psa 115:4</a><p/><b>Perishable</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=40&verse=20'>Isa 40:20</a><p/><b>Helpless</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=45&verse=20'>Isa 45:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=10&verse=5'>Jer 10:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=18'>Act 14:18</a><p/><b>Unworthy of Worship</b> of Intelligent Beings<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=29'>Ac 17:29</a><p/><b>Degrading</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=22'>Rom 1:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=23'>Rom 1:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=8&verse=4'>1Co 8:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=12&verse=2'>1Co 12:2</a><p/><b>(4) Examples of</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=4'>Exo 32:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=25&verse=2'>Num 25:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=3&verse=7'>Jdg 3:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=32'>1Ki 12:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=31'>1Ki 16:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=12'>2Ki 17:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=21&verse=21'>2Ki 21:21</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=25&verse=14'>2Ch 25:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=2'>2Ch 28:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=3&verse=7'>Dan 3:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=23'>Dan 5:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=16'>Act 17:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=4&verse=8'>Gal 4:8</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> False Gods, FALSE WORSHIP<p/><b>(5) Making of Idols</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=40&verse=19'>Isa 40:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=44&verse=10'>Isa 44:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=46&verse=6'>Isa 46:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=10&verse=3'>Jer 10:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=7&verse=20'>Eze 7:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=17'>Eze 16:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=22&verse=3'>Eze 22:3</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=3&verse=1'>Dan 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=8&verse=4'>Hos 8:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=13&verse=2'>Hos 13:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=35&chapter=2&verse=18'>Hab 2:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=24'>Act 19:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=23'>Rom 1:23</a><p/><b>(6) Vanity of</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=10&verse=5'>Jer 10:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=10&verse=15'>Jer 10:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=50&verse=38'>Jer 50:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=17'>Jer 51:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=23'>Dan 5:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=35&chapter=2&verse=18'>Hab 2:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=29'>Act 17:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=10&verse=19'>1Co 10:19</a><p/><b>(B) FALSE GODS AND GODDESSES, General References to</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=26'>1Ch 16:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=2&verse=8'>Isa 2:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=2&verse=11'>Jer 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=11&verse=12'>Jer 11:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=16&verse=20'>Jer 16:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=4'>Dan 5:4</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=8&verse=5'>1Co 8:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=12&verse=2'>1Co 12:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=4&verse=8'>Gal 4:8</a><p/><b>ASHTAROTH</b> or <b>ASHTORETH,</b> a goddess of the Phoenicians<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=2&verse=13'>Jdg 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=10&verse=6'>Jdg 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=3'>1Sa 7:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=10'>1Sa 31:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=33'>1Ki 11:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=13'>2Ki 23:13</a><p/><b>BAAL</b> a god of Phoenicia and the Canaanitish Tribes<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=22&verse=41'>Num 22:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=2&verse=11'>Jdg 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=33'>Jdg 8:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=32'>1Ki 16:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=19'>1Ki 18:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=18'>1Ki 19:18</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=18'>2Ki 10:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=28'>2Ki 10:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=21&verse=3'>2Ki 21:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=24&verse=7'>2Ch 24:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=2&verse=8'>Jer 2:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=9'>Jer 7:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=2&verse=8'>Hos 2:8</a><p/><b>BAAL-PEOR,</b> a god of the Moabites<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=25&verse=3'>Num 25:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=4&verse=3'>Deu 4:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=22&verse=17'>Jos 22:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=28'>Psa 106:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=9&verse=10'>Hos 9:10</a><p/><b>CHEMOSH,</b> a god of the Moabites<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=21&verse=29'>Num 21:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=24'>Jdg 11:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=13'>2Ki 23:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=7'>Jer 48:7</a><p/><b>DAGON,</b> a god of the Philistines<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=16&verse=23'>Jdg 16:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=5&verse=2'>1Sa 5:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=10&verse=10'>1Ch 10:10</a><p/><b>DIANA,</b> a goddess of the Ephesians<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=24'>Act 19:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=28'>Act 19:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=35'>Act 19:35</a><p/><b>MOLECH,</b> Moloch, or Milcom, a god of the Ammonites<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=18&verse=21'>Lev 18:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=10'>2Ki 23:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=32&verse=35'>Jer 32:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=5&verse=26'>Amo 5:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=43'>Act 7:43</a><p/><b>(C) OTHER OBJECTS OF WORSHIP</b><p/><b>(1) The Golden Calf</b> made by Aaron<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=4'>Exo 32:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=16'>Deu 9:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=9&verse=18'>Neh 9:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=19'>Psa 106:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=41'>Act 7:41</a><p/><b>(2) The Golden Calves of Jeroboam,</b> set up in Dan and Bethel<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=28'>1Ki 12:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=29'>2Ki 10:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=16'>2Ki 17:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=15'>2Ch 11:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13&verse=8'>2Ch 13:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=10&verse=5'>Hos 10:5</a><p/><b>(3) Heavenly Bodies</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=4&verse=19'>Deu 4:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=3'>Deu 17:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=16'>2Ki 17:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=21&verse=3'>2Ki 21:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=31&verse=26'>Job 31:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=8&verse=2'>Jer 8:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=19&verse=13'>Jer 19:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=44&verse=17'>Jer 44:17</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=8&verse=16'>Eze 8:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=1&verse=5'>Zep 1:5</a><p/><b>(4) Teraphim,</b> images, household gods<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=19'>Gen 31:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=34'>Gen 31:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=17&verse=5'>Jdg 17:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=18&verse=14'>Jdg 18:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=19&verse=13'>1Sa 19:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=3&verse=4'>Hos 3:4</a><p/><b>(5) Men Deified</b> and Worshipped<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=22'>Act 12:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=11'>Act 14:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=28&verse=6'>Act 28:6</a><p/><b>(6) Devils Worshipped</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=17&verse=7'>Lev 17:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=17'>Deu 32:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=15'>2Ch 11:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=37'>Psa 106:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=10&verse=20'>1Co 10:20</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=9&verse=20'>Rev 9:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=13&verse=4'>Rev 13:4</a><p/>-- Brazen Serpent. See BRAZEN SERPENT<p/><b>(D) PLACES DEVOTED TO IDOLATRY</b><p/><b>(1) Idolatrous Altars</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=32'>1Ki 16:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=26'>1Ki 18:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=27&verse=9'>Isa 27:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=65&verse=3'>Isa 65:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=8&verse=11'>Hos 8:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=23'>Act 17:23</a><p/><b>(2) Idolatrous Temples</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=5&verse=2'>1Sa 5:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=31'>1Ki 12:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=18'>2Ki 5:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=21'>2Ki 10:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=7'>2Ch 36:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=2'>Dan 1:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=27'>Act 19:27</a><p/><b>(3) High Places</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=22&verse=41'>Num 22:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=7'>1Ki 11:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=31'>1Ki 12:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=9'>2Ki 17:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=29'>2Ki 17:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=18&verse=4'>2Ki 18:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=21&verse=3'>2Ki 21:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=5'>2Ki 23:5</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=15'>2Ch 11:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=17&verse=6'>2Ch 17:6</a><p/><b>(4) Groves</b> (Asherah or Asherim) places where shrines were located<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=12&verse=2'>Deu 12:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=21'>Deu 16:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=25'>Jdg 6:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=15'>1Ki 14:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=33'>1Ki 16:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=18&verse=4'>2Ki 18:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=21&verse=3'>2Ki 21:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=14'>2Ki 23:14</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=14&verse=3'>2Ch 14:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=17&verse=6'>2Ch 17:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=17&verse=8'>Isa 17:8</a>"}]}